EU’s Rehn Says Euro-Area Risks Remain Tilted to the Downside

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-09-15T09:31:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/eu-s-rehn-says-euro-area-risks-remain-tilted-to-the-downside.html
Risks to the growth outlook for the
euro area are “tilted to the downside,” European Union
Economic and Monetary Commissioner  Olli Rehn  told reporters in
Brussels today.  Financial turmoil is harming the economic recovery, Rehn
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Clapham at 
 aclapham@bloomberg.net  